creator: Cookpad Inc (UK)
descriptionHtml:
If you love home cooking, discovering new ideas, and sharing your inspirations with others then Cookpad is the place for you.

Cooking at home can sometimes feel lonely, and it can be hard to find daily motivations, but with nearly 3 million recipes, the world’s largest community of active cooks, and the ability to save a collection, you won’t struggle for new ideas.

Enjoy these Cookpad app features:

- Add your recipes and share with fellow Cookpad users
- Explore an always fresh feed of latest recipes from cooks you follow
- Plan what you are going to cook next with a daily meal planner
- A list of your cooked recipes so you’ll never forget the things you’ve enjoyed
- Keep track of changes you make each time you cook with Cooking logs. On each recipe - see who is cooking your recipe in real-time and follow the cooking conversation from the community and see any changes they make.
- Search recipes by food title or multiple ingredients.

Find daily inspiration

Across our global network, Cookpad recipe creators add thousands of new
recipes every week so there will always be something that provides a spark of inspiration. Never miss out with a feed of recipes from the cooks you follow.

Building your cooking plan and collection

As you discover new ideas you can now easily save them into a daily cookplan. So when you’ve decided what you want to cook next, planning and preparing has never been easier.

And once you cook something, you can now mark it as “cooked”. This means it is then saved in your cooked recipes list. With busy lives, it is all too easy to forget those meals that you enjoyed in the past. Well, with the “cooked” feature you won’t have that problem.

Join the world’s most active cooking community

The best way to enjoy Cookpad is to share the highlights, discoveries and the recipes of the food you love to cook. With our easy-to-use recipe creation tool, you can add your recipes, ideas and photos in minutes.

And the best feeling is when someone cooks and enjoys your recipe. Each recipe on Cookpad has its own cooking history. We call this the Cooking Log and it’s where you can see who else has enjoyed that recipe, see their tips and learn how they’ve made changes and see the results!

This is what makes Cookpad special - you too can enjoy cooking more through inspiring and being inspired by others.

Cookpad is the world's largest homemade recipe-sharing app and is currently available in more than 20 languages with communities in more than 70 countries.

Cookpad has already helped millions of people to:

Discover new recipes
Build connections with other cooks.
Gain confidence in their cooking abilities.

Come join us 💜
descriptionShort: Find inspiration and share your recipes and love of cooking

This is what makes Cookpad special - you too can enjoy cooking more through inspiring and being inspired by others.

Discover new recipes

title: Cookpad - Create your own Recipes

creator: Cookpad Inc (UK)
descriptionHtml:
If you love home cooking, discovering new ideas, and sharing your inspirations with others then Cookpad is the place for you.

Cooking at home can sometimes feel lonely, and it can be hard to find daily motivations, but with nearly 3 million recipes, the world’s largest community of active cooks, and the ability to save a collection, you won’t struggle for new ideas.

Enjoy these Cookpad app features:

- Add your recipes and share with fellow Cookpad users
- Explore an always fresh feed of latest recipes from cooks you follow
- Plan what you are going to cook next with a daily meal planner
- A list of your cooked recipes so you’ll never forget the things you’ve enjoyed
- Keep track of changes you make each time you cook with Cooking logs. On each recipe - see who is cooking your recipe in real-time and follow the cooking conversation from the community and see any changes they make.
- Search recipes by food title or multiple ingredients.

Find daily inspiration

Across our global network, Cookpad recipe creators add thousands of new
recipes every week so there will always be something that provides a spark of inspiration. Never miss out with a feed of recipes from the cooks you follow.

Building your cooking plan and collection

As you discover new ideas you can now easily save them into a daily cookplan. So when you’ve decided what you want to cook next, planning and preparing has never been easier.

And once you cook something, you can now mark it as “cooked”. This means it is then saved in your cooked recipes list. With busy lives, it is all too easy to forget those meals that you enjoyed in the past. Well, with the “cooked” feature you won’t have that problem.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Thanks for using Cookpad!
We’ve made changes to the navigation bar to make it easier to find our most important features - there are now five tabs instead of three, including a dedicated tab for ‘Search’ and ‘Activity’
We’ve replaced the ‘Plan’ tab with a new ‘You’ tab and all of your recipes that were saved in the ‘Plan’ will appear in ‘You’
This update also includes general bug fixes and improvements to make your experience better than ever before!

Each Cookpad recipe has been created, tried and tested by home cooks, for home cooks so whether you love to create, or just want to cook, Cookpad is the place for you.

- Browse a diverse collection of recipes, or search by specifics - ingredients, seasonal dishes, holiday favourites and more
- Create and share your own recipes and help others to become better cooks
- Share photos (or cooksnaps) of the recipes you cook and inspire others to try them too
- Connect with other home cooks, ask questions and share ideas
- Build a limitless collection of recipes you find, share and cook - it’s your own personal cookbook

Please contact us if you need any further information or help at help@cookpad.com
descriptionShort: Find inspiration and share your recipes and love of cooking

title: Cookpad: Find & Share Recipes

creator: Cookpad Inc (UK)
descriptionHtml:
Do you like to cook? Are you looking for step-wise recipes? Are you a home chef?
Yes? Then Cookpad is for you!

Cookpad is a recipe sharing community on a mission to improve people’s lives by making everyday home cooking more fun.

With Cookpad, you will get access to over 5,00,000 free recipes, which have been uploaded by expert home chefs and home cooks, like yourself. Find multiple recipes across 6 different languages, which include: English, Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, and Bengali.

Cookpad is much more than an app for searching and viewing recipes. On Cookpad you can also:
- Save/Bookmark recipes
- Comment on and like recipes
- Upload your own recipes
- Store and save all your recipes digitally in one place
- Share Cooking/Food/Kitchen Tips with the community
- Follow other home chefs and home cooks

On Cookpad App, you get to view: English Recipes, Hindi Recipes, Bengali Recipes, Gujarati Recipes, Marathi Recipes, and Tamil Recipes.

Other than recipes, if you join Cookpad, then you also get to:
- Take part in fun and challenging recipe writing challenges
- Meet us and other home chefs from your city/state in our Offline Community Meet-ups/Events
- Learn cooking from experts and masterchefs
- Attend live cooking demos on Facebook and exclusive live sessions on Zoom

Cookpad loves people who love to cook and that's why Cookpad showcases, promotes, and shares selected recipes on the app, website, and social media, on a daily basis, making them reach thousands of people.

Cookpad is the best app for home chefs, home cooks, food lovers, and cooking experts.
Cookpad facilitates sharing and is a community where you can get to know other foodies, interact with them, ask questions, share a photo of the dish you made following someone's recipe and grow together by learning from one another.

Did you know?: If you upload your recipes on Cookpad, then they also show up on Google search.

Join our circle of food lovers by downloading the app today to view and upload recipes in English, recipes in Hindi, recipes in Bengali, recipes in Tamil, and recipes in Gujarati.

Sign up, log on, and get cooking!

For any queries or suggestions, write to us on info-in@cookpad.com.
descriptionShort: Share and search simple recipes and cooking tips for home chefs

title: Cookpad: Find & Share Recipes

creator: Cookpad Inc (UK)
descriptionHtml:
Do you like to cook? Are you looking for step-wise recipes? Are you a home chef?
Yes? Then Cookpad is for you!

Cookpad is a recipe sharing community on a mission to improve people’s lives by making everyday home cooking more fun.

With Cookpad, you will get access to over 5,00,000 free recipes, which have been uploaded by expert home chefs and home cooks, like yourself. Find multiple recipes across 6 different languages, which include: English, Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, and Bengali.

Cookpad is much more than an app for searching and viewing recipes. On Cookpad you can also:
- Save/Bookmark recipes
- Comment on and like recipes
- Upload your own recipes
- Store and save all your recipes digitally in one place
- Share Cooking/Food/Kitchen Tips with the community
- Follow other home chefs and home cooks

On Cookpad App, you get to view: English Recipes, Hindi Recipes, Bengali Recipes, Gujarati Recipes, Marathi Recipes, and Tamil Recipes.

Other than recipes, if you join Cookpad, then you also get to:
- Take part in fun and challenging recipe writing challenges
- Meet us and other home chefs from your city/state in our Offline Community Meet-ups/Events
- Learn cooking from experts and masterchefs
- Attend live cooking demos on Facebook and exclusive live sessions on Zoom

Cookpad loves people who love to cook and that's why Cookpad showcases, promotes, and shares selected recipes on the app, website, and social media, on a daily basis, making them reach thousands of people.

Cookpad is the best app for home chefs, home cooks, food lovers, and cooking experts.
Cookpad facilitates sharing and is a community where you can get to know other foodies, interact with them, ask questions, share a photo of the dish you made following someone's recipe and grow together by learning from one another.

Did you know?: If you upload your recipes on Cookpad, then they also show up on Google search.

Join our circle of food lovers by downloading the app today to view and upload recipes in English, recipes in Hindi, recipes in Bengali, recipes in Tamil, and recipes in Gujarati.

Sign up, log on, and get cooking!

For any queries or suggestions, write to us on info-in@cookpad.com.
descriptionShort: Share and search simple recipes and cooking tips for home chefs

Bored of cooking the same thing week in, week out?

Looking for new variations on your family’s favourite dishes?

Want tasty, everyday ways to use up the ingredients in your fridge?

Looking for everyday cooks like you to share tips, ideas and recipes?

Have you tried Cookpad?

Cookpad is a global recipe-sharing platform and cooking community, where people like you come to browse, search, create and share thousands of home-cooked recipes everyday.

• Stuck in a rut? Find thousands of new, easy variations on your family’s favourite dishes to cook any day of the week, shared by home cooks for home cooks.

• Cook for fussy eaters and intolerances. Whatever your family’s preferences or dietary requirements, whether vegetarian, dairy-free, gluten-free or Keto, or you're looking for healthy options, you can keep the whole family happy. Search and use filters to find the recipes you want.

• Clear out your fridge and use up leftovers easily by searching for recipes based on your ingredients. Want a recipe with pasta, chicken and broccoli? Type all of your ingredients into the search bar and find variations on your favourite dishes.

• Learn something new! Browse ideas and new inspiration whatever the season. Don’t know how to use up those winter root vegetables? Planning your menu for Christmas, Easter or Mother’s Day? Let our community help you.

• Get help from cooks just like you. Connect with a lively community of passionate home cooks and make new friends around the world. Take part in cooking challenges and online cooking classes, ask questions and exchange advice.

• Create your own recipe book, share your own recipes, tips and ideas and help other cooks make delicious, easy, everyday recipes.

• Cook from recipes all written with step-by-step instructions, photos and tips, each one tried and tested by home cooks like you.

Want to join us? Download the app, come and cook with us.

*Find tried and tested recipes more easily with Cookpad Premium*

Premium is Cookpad’s subscription service. It makes finding delicious recipes even easier.

Simply search for a recipe or ingredient in the normal way, and you’ll find the recipes our community loves the most first, instead of those most recently published.

There are lots of other great benefits too - including Premium search filters and exclusive access to our recipe Hall of Fame. This is where the community’s best-loved recipes are celebrated. Spend less time searching and more time enjoying what you cook with Premium.

Cookpad Premium is currently available in Arabic speaking countries, Argentina, Greece, Hungary, Indonesia, Malaysia, Mexico, Russia, Spain, Taiwan, Thailand, Uruguay and Vietnam.

Get in touch with us: help@cookpad.com
descriptionShort: Find inspiration, share your recipes and love of cooking

title: Cookpad: Find & Share Recipes

creator: Cookpad Inc (UK)
descriptionHtml:
Do you like to cook? Are you looking for step-wise recipes? Are you a home chef?
Yes? Then Cookpad is for you!

Cookpad is a recipe sharing community on a mission to improve people’s lives by making everyday home cooking more fun.

With Cookpad, you will get access to over 5,00,000 free recipes, which have been uploaded by expert home chefs and home cooks, like yourself. Find multiple recipes across 6 different languages, which include: English, Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, and Bengali.

Cookpad is much more than an app for searching and viewing recipes. On Cookpad you can also:
- Save/Bookmark recipes
- Comment on and like recipes
- Upload your own recipes
- Store and save all your recipes digitally in one place
- Share Cooking/Food/Kitchen Tips with the community
- Follow other home chefs and home cooks

On Cookpad App, you get to view: English Recipes, Hindi Recipes, Bengali Recipes, Gujarati Recipes, Marathi Recipes, and Tamil Recipes.

Other than recipes, if you join Cookpad, then you also get to:
- Take part in fun and challenging recipe writing challenges
- Meet us and other home chefs from your city/state in our Offline Community Meet-ups/Events
- Learn cooking from experts and masterchefs
- Attend live cooking demos on Facebook and exclusive live sessions on Zoom

Cookpad loves people who love to cook and that's why Cookpad showcases, promotes, and shares selected recipes on the app, website, and social media, on a daily basis, making them reach thousands of people.

Cookpad is the best app for home chefs, home cooks, food lovers, and cooking experts.
Cookpad facilitates sharing and is a community where you can get to know other foodies, interact with them, ask questions, share a photo of the dish you made following someone's recipe and grow together by learning from one another.

Did you know?: If you upload your recipes on Cookpad, then they also show up on Google search.

Join our circle of food lovers by downloading the app today to view and upload recipes in English, recipes in Hindi, recipes in Bengali, recipes in Tamil, and recipes in Gujarati.

Sign up, log on, and get cooking!

For any queries or suggestions, write to us on info-in@cookpad.com.
descriptionShort: Share and search simple recipes and cooking tips for home chefs

Looking for new variations on your family’s favourite dishes?

Want tasty, everyday ways to use up the ingredients in your fridge?

Seeking everyday cooks like you to share cooking tips and recipes?

Have you tried Cookpad?

• Stuck in a rut? Find easy variations on your family’s favourite dishes.

• Cater for your whole family. Use filters to find recipes for fussy eaters and intolerances, whether vegetarian, dairy-free, gluten-free or Keto, and so much more.

• Search by ingredients so you can easily use up what’s in your fridge.

• Get help from cooks just like you. Connect with a lively community of passionate home cooks.

• Share your recipes and tips and help other cooks make delicious, easy, everyday recipes.

Get in touch with us: help@cookpad.com

Bored of cooking the same thing week in, week out?

Looking for new variations on your family’s favorite dishes?

Want tasty, everyday ways to use up the ingredients in your fridge?

Seeking everyday cooks like you to share cooking tips and recipes?

Have you tried Cookpad?

• Stuck in a rut? Find lots of different ideas to prepare your family's favorite ingredients.

• We’re strictly advert-free! Browse and search recipes free of interruption.




Spend less time searching and more time enjoying what you cook with Cookpad’s subscription service, Premium:

• Discover the community’s most popular, tested recipes faster, with Premium Search

• Save unlimited recipes so you never run out of inspiration again

• Filter recipes to match your preferences

Cookpad Premium is available in Arabic speaking countries, Argentina, Brazil, Chile, Colombia, France, Greece, Hungary, India (English only), Indonesia, Italy, Malaysia, Mexico, Romania, Spain, Taiwan, Thailand, Ukraine, United Kingdom, United States, Uruguay and Vietnam.

Looking for new variations on your family’s favorite dishes?

Want tasty, everyday ways to use up the ingredients in your fridge?

Seeking everyday cooks like you to share cooking tips and recipes?

Have you tried Cookpad?

Cookpad is a global recipe-sharing platform and cooking community. Here, people like you come to find and share tonnes of home-cooked recipes everyday.

• Stuck in a rut? Find lots of different ideas to prepare your family's favorite ingredients.

• Cater for your whole family. Use filters to find recipes for fussy eaters and intolerances, whether vegetarian, dairy-free, gluten-free or Keto, and so much more.

• Search by ingredients so you can easily use up what’s in your fridge.

• Get help from cooks just like you. Connect with a lively community of passionate home cooks.

• Share your recipes and tips and help other cooks make delicious, easy, everyday recipes.

• We’re strictly advert-free! Browse and search recipes free of interruption.




Spend less time searching and more time enjoying what you cook with Cookpad’s subscription service, Premium:

• Discover the community’s most popular, tested recipes faster, with Premium Search

• Save unlimited recipes so you never run out of inspiration again

• Filter recipes to match your preferences

Cookpad Premium is available in Arabic speaking countries, Argentina, Brazil, Chile, Colombia, France, Greece, Hungary, India (English only), Indonesia, Italy, Malaysia, Mexico, Romania, Spain, Taiwan, Thailand, Ukraine, United Kingdom, United States, Uruguay and Vietnam.

Get in touch with us: help@cookpad.com
descriptionShort: Share your recipes, find daily cooking inspiration and join a cooking community

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New features this week:
◾️ Step-by-step videos now play automatically!
The step-by-step videos in the recipe details will now play automatically, so you don’t need to tap the screen while cooking to start playback.

Cookpad is actively improving the app. To fully utilize the latest features and fixes, please update to the latest version.

If you have any feedback, go to Profile > Send feedback in the app!
